This is a next.js project with polkadot-api(papi) and kheopskit wallet integration.

If any major code changes follow @ui.mdc rules for best practices.

## Testing Changes with pnpm dev

When implementing changes or fixes, always test them using the development server:

1. **Start Development Server**: Run `pnpm dev` to start the Next.js development server with Turbopack
2. **Check Server Status**: Verify the server is running on the default port (3000) or handle port conflicts
3. **Monitor Console**: Watch for any runtime errors or warnings in the browser console and terminal
